## 2. index.html Scaffold

**Pattern:** copy head + structure from `public/demos/construction-company-website/index.html` (single-file, Google Fonts CDN, no bundler). Then replace all content. Do NOT import any michaelwegter.com palette tokens.

**Google Fonts CDN link (exact):**
```html
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,600&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
```

**Required DOM IDs** (app.js uses `const $ = id => document.getElementById(id)` + querySelector):

| ID / selector | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `#btn-run` | Run Scraper button — adds class `running`, gets disabled |
| `#btn-export` | Export JSON download — disabled during scrape |
| `#btn-view-all` | Open full dataset in inspector |
| `#lots-grid` | Card grid container |
| `#filter-source` | `<select>` — values: `all`, `leland_little`, `heritage_auctions`, `bonhams` |
| `#filter-has-image` | `<input type="checkbox">` |
| `#filter-est-max` | `<input type="range" min="0" max="500000" step="1000">` |
| `#est-max-label` | Text node showing current max estimate |
| `#sort-select` | `<select>` — values: `default`, `date`, `estimate_low`, `estimate_high`, `source` |
| `#status-total` | Inline text: "X of Y lots" |
| `#telemetry-log` | Scrolling log container — gets class `open` when visible |
| `#telemetry-count` | Log line count badge |
| `#inspector-overlay` | Full-screen modal overlay — gets class `open` |
| `#inspector-title` | Inspector heading (lot title) |
| `#inspector-body` | Pre-formatted JSON content area |
| `#btn-close-inspector` | Close inspector button |
| `#btn-copy-json` | Copy JSON to clipboard |
| `.inspector-tab[data-tab="normalized"]` | Tab button |
| `.inspector-tab[data-tab="raw_json_ld"]` | Tab button (display:none for non-Heritage lots) |
| `#lightbox` | Lightbox modal — gets class `open` |
| `#lb-img` | `<img>` inside lightbox |
| `#lb-caption` | Caption text |
| `#lb-counter` | "1 / 3" counter |
| `#lb-prev` | `<button>` previous |
| `#lb-next` | `<button>` next |
| `#btn-close-lb` | Close lightbox |
| `#dataset-bar` | Summary bar after job_done — gets class `visible` |
| `#dataset-summary` | Inner text: "18 lots collected — 8 from Heritage…" |
| `#toast` | Toast notification div — gets class `show` |
| `.source-status[data-source="leland_little"]` | Source row — gets `data-state` attr (idle/running/done/flagged/error) |
| `.source-status[data-source="heritage_auctions"]` | Source row |
| `.source-status[data-source="bonhams"]` | Source row |
| `.source-status-badge` (inside each row) | Badge text — states: Idle, Running, Done, Flagged, Error |
| `.source-status-meta` (inside each row) | Meta text: tool name then lot count |
| `.source-cb` (3 checkboxes) | Values: `leland_little`, `heritage_auctions`, `bonhams` — checked by default |
| `.telemetry-header` | Clickable header div (attaches click listener for toggle) |
| `.telemetry-toggle` | Toggle button text (▲ Hide / ▼ Show) |

**Script tag** (end of body): `<script src="app.js"></script>`

