## 6. Backend Deploy Instructions

Blueprint is registered locally (server.py:341–342) but NOT live — live endpoint returns 404. Flask is running on Surface.

Deploy path (CLAUDE.md §1):
```bash
cd ../mw-backend
git add auction_scraper_blueprint.py auction_scraper_seeds.json server.py
git commit -m "Add auction-scraper blueprint and seeds"
git push
# Wait ~30s, then verify:
curl https://api.michaelwegter.com/demos/auction-scraper/health
# Expected: {"ok":true,"playwright_available":...,"seeds_loaded":{"heritage":8,...}}
```

